{"tid":1249273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講個歷史故事你聽 「十面埋伏」","createTime":"2019-06-21T16:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T16:39:02.000Z","uid":1251,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd41fba2acc96b472bed8651fe9b84052bf4229","tid":1249273,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"秦亡，楚漢互爭天下，西楚霸王項羽神勇而寡謀，且剛愎自用，聽信漢軍元帥韓信派來詐降的李左車之言，不顧眾將與愛妃虞姬勸阻，起兵伐漢，率大軍直入九里山，中韓信誘兵之計，陷入十面埋伏，被困於垓下。<span style=\"color: red;\">漢營又命軍卒學作楚歌，楚將楚兵聞之，以為漢軍已得楚地，皆動思鄉之念，大部離散。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">冇得返屋企又掛住屋企<br />\n精神會變得好脆弱<br />\n係時候轉軟攻<br />\n有冇絲打有聲優既聲線call下咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f1bf315e61da88e520bc10a367945372402a465a","tid":1249273,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26143395fb9bdbc0e9bebb3da4524e449bbf255c","tid":1249273,"uid":266343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd41fba2acc96b472bed8651fe9b84052bf4229","tid":1249273,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"秦亡，楚漢互爭天下，西楚霸王項羽神勇而寡謀，且剛愎自用，聽信漢軍元帥韓信派來詐降的李左車之言，不顧眾將與愛妃虞姬勸阻，起兵伐漢，率大軍直入九里山，中韓信誘兵之計，陷入十面埋伏，被困於垓下。<span style=\"color: red;\">漢營又命軍卒學作楚歌，楚將楚兵聞之，以為漢軍已得楚地，皆動思鄉之念，大部離散。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">冇得返屋企又掛住屋企<br />\n精神會變得好脆弱<br />\n係時候轉軟攻<br />\n有冇絲打有聲優既聲線call下咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"我想聽周庭call咪👉🏻👈🏻"},{"pid":"f380f102c63696d8ac7da0f3cfc8c0dcc68f3200","tid":1249273,"uid":1251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"26143395f